    "patch_code": "public static void main(String[] args){\n\t\tDateTime dateTime=new DateTime();  \n    \n    //corrected src/main/java/org/joda/time/format/PeriodFormatter.java\n    System.out.println(PeriodFormatterBuilder.getDateOnlyInstance().print(new DurationFieldType[]{DurationFieldType.years(),DurationFieldType.months(),DurationFieldType.days()}, new int[]{3,4,5}));\n        \n    //incorrect src/main/java/org/joda/time/format/PeriodFormatter.java\n    String out= new PeriodFormatterBuilder()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('P')\n\t\t\t\t.appendYears()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('Y')\n\t\t\t\t.appendSuffix(\"and \")\n\t\t\t\t.appendMonths()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('M')\n\t\t\t\t.appendSuffix(\" and some \")\n\t\t\t\t.appendDays()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('D')\n\t\t\t\t.appendSeparatorIfFieldsAfter(\" \")\n\t\t\t\t.appendHours()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('h')\n\t\t\t\t.appendMinutes()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('m')\n\t\t\t\t.appendSecondsWithOptionalMillis()\n\t\t\t\t.appendLiteral('s')\n\t\t\t\t.toFormatter()\n                .print(3,7,9);\n\t\t     \n\t    System.out.println(out);\n\t}",
