    "patch_code": "public static void main(String[] args) {\n\tDateTime dateTime = new DateTime();\n\tPeriod period = new Period(dateTime, new DateTime().plusMonths(3).plusDays(5));\n\n\t// correct version\n\tPeriodFormatter fmt;\n\tfmt = new PeriodFormatterBuilder()\n\t\t\t.printZeroAlways()\n\t\t\t.minimumPrintedDigits(2)\n\t\t\t.appendYears().appendText(\" year(s) \")\n\t\t\t.appendMonths().appendText(\" month(s) \")\n\t\t\t.appendWeeks().appendText(\" week(s) \")\n\t\t\t.appendDays().appendText(\" day(s) \")\n\t\t\t.appendSeparator(\" \")\n\t\t\t.appendHours() .appendText(\" hour(s) \")\n\t\t\t.appendMinutes().appendText(\" minute(s) \")\n\t\t\t.appendSecondsWithOptionalMillis().appendText(\" second(s)\")\n\t\t\t.toFormatter();\n\n\tString formatted = fmt.print(period);\n\tSystem.out.println(formatted);\n\n\t// wrong version\n\tPeriodFormatter pfmt2 = ISOPeriodFormat.standard().withZone(DateTimeZone.forID(\"GMT+8\")).toFormatter();\n\tpfmt2.setLocale(new Locale(\"zh\", \"CN\"));\n\tString s = pfmt2.print(1);\n\tSystem.out.println(s);\n\t}",
